<p align="center">An advanced padding oracle attack tool with enhanced terminal interface</p>

---

## ✨ Features

- 🎨 Modern terminal interface with animations
- 🌈 Color-coded menus and status indicators
- 📊 Real-time progress tracking
- 🔧 Interactive settings management
- 📝 Comprehensive logging
- 🔍 Multiple attack modes

## 🚀 Quick Start

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/padbuster.git

# Install dependencies
cpan Term::ANSIColor Term::ReadKey

# Run PadBuster
./padbuster.pl URL EncryptedSample BlockSize
```

## 📋 Usage Examples

### Basic Decryption
```bash
./padbuster.pl https://target.com/app encrypted_data 16
```

### With Authentication
```bash
./padbuster.pl https://target.com/app encrypted_data 16 -auth user:pass
```

## 🎯 Attack Modes

| Mode | Description | Usage |
|------|-------------|-------|
| 🔓 Decrypt | Decrypt encrypted values | Basic mode |
| 🔒 Encrypt | Encrypt custom data | Use -plaintext |
| 🔨 Brute Force | Force decrypt unknown data | Use -bruteforce |

## 🔧 Configuration

The tool can be configured using various command-line options:

```bash
Options:
  -auth [user:pass]    : HTTP Basic Authentication
  -proxy [host:port]   : Use HTTP/S Proxy
  -cookies [data]      : Custom cookies
  -headers [data]      : Custom headers
```

## 🎨 Themes

PadBuster Enhanced Edition comes with multiple terminal themes:

- 🌞 Light Theme
- 🌙 Dark Theme
- 🌈 Rainbow Theme
- 🎨 Custom Theme

